    "Equation 18 is the calculation process of the IoU.",
    "where P is the predicted bounding box and G is the groundtruth bounding box.",
    "This is a summary of the prediction results, where TP represents the number of predictions that will be positive to positive classes.",
    "FN differs from TP in that it is the number of positive classes predicted as negative classes.",
    "FP is the exact opposite of FN, and it is the number of negative classes predicted as positive classes."
